{#
=============================================================================
EXAMPLE RENDERINGS
=============================================================================

{{ forensic_declarative("the body", "was discovered", "in the library at a quarter past eight") }}
→ "The body was discovered in the library at a quarter past eight."

{{ free_indirect_interrogation("Mrs. Thornton", "I was in the drawing room all evening. I heard nothing at all.", "the drawing room windows face the library, and she had always known precisely which windows faced which rooms") }}
→
"I was in the drawing room all evening. I heard nothing at all," Mrs. Thornton said.
But what Mrs. Thornton did not say — what Mrs. Thornton could not bring
themselves to say, even to themselves — was that the drawing room windows face the library, and she had always known precisely which windows faced which rooms.

{{ widening_ripple("The Colonel was murdered in his library on a Tuesday evening in October", "Mrs. Thornton, who had served him tea at four and would now be asked to account for every teaspoon.", "The verger, who had passed the library window at dusk and seen nothing — except that he had seen nothing, which was itself a thing to be seen.", "The young woman from the village, whose name no one in the house could quite recall, but who had been seen walking in the direction of the house at an hour when no young woman from the village had any reason to be walking in that direction.") }}
→
The Colonel was murdered in his library on a Tuesday evening in October.
Mrs. Thornton, who had served him tea at four and would now be asked to account for every teaspoon.
The verger, who had passed the library window at dusk and seen nothing — except that he had seen nothing, which was itself a thing to be seen.
The young woman from the village, whose name no one in the house could quite recall, but who had been seen walking in the direction of the house at an hour when no young woman from the village had any reason to be walking in that direction.
And this was only the beginning — the first ring of a disturbance whose full circumference no one present could yet measure.

{{ distributed_verdict("The Major", "half the village had known something was wrong and had chosen, one after another, in small daily acts of convenience, not to ask", "The widow forgave no one. The village learned nothing. The house was sold.") }}
→
The Major was guilty. The facts permitted no other conclusion.
But what the facts could not capture was that half the village had known something was wrong and had chosen, one after another, in small daily acts of convenience, not to ask.
The widow forgave no one. The village learned nothing. The house was sold.
The verdict was clear. The clarity was not the same thing as healing.

{{ system_prompt("A body is discovered in the library of a country house. Write the opening scene.", [], 0.20) }}
→ The full system prompt with the two-layer MoE architecture.

=============================================================================
#}
